title: IAA Tonight | Dak and Zion are Back!
description: Dak Prescott is back and ready to start for the Cowboys against the Lions this Sunday, but is he fully ready to go? One host believes he should rest a few more weeks. Plus, Zion Williamson is back and looks like he's in incredible shape after his outstanding performance against the Brooklyn Nets on Wednesday. How good is this Pelicans squad with Brandon Ingram and CJ McCollum?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Brandon Marshall, Adam Pacman Jones)
